{"tid":2015180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"專治武肺醫院失火5死 23萬確診超英趕美 普京堅持全俄復工","createTime":"2020-05-13T13:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T13:24:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6d99d485eb9f3831721d35284d61f5b599a972ac","tid":2015180,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T13:11:17.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200513/Z2JLUA5KADFNNZ552YF6OK5FZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200513%2FZ2JLUA5KADFNNZ552YF6OK5FZ4%2F&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=774c6e2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200513%2FZ2JLUA5KADFNNZ552YF6OK5FZ4%2F&h=a9364cc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200513/Z2JLUA5KADFNNZ552YF6OK5FZ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n專治武肺醫院失火5死 23萬確診超英趕美<br />\n普京堅持全俄復工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200513/large/1589299627_a36f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200513%2Flarge%2F1589299627_a36f.gif&h=6058f152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肇事醫院的玻璃窗損毀、牆身熏黑。&lt;br /&gt;法新社<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯的武漢肺炎疫情未有止勢，累計逾23萬宗確診，人數超越西班牙和英國，成為全球繼美國之後第二多人感染的國家；惟總統普京反其道而行，宣佈全國昨日起逐步復工；另外，近日多間抗疫醫院起火，其中第二大城市聖彼德堡一家醫院昨疑因呼吸器短路失火，燒死5名病人。<br />\n<br />\n普京前日以嚴肅表情發表電視講話，公佈自3月底頒令的全國休業限令，由昨日起「逐步而小心地」解禁。他強調醫療部。。。。。。。。。。。撥資源抗疫，病院接收的染疫病人由29,000人增至13萬人，「挽救數以千計人的性命」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n普京發言人確診<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：抗疫「不合格」普京頭痕<br />\n<br />\n普京又強調為保就業、為了大眾利益，經濟發展就要盡快恢復正常，尤其是。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n區可按需要延長限制。<br />\n<br />\n他又建議地方政府容許人民外出散步和運動，但強調疫情還未結束，65歲或以上長者或長期病人應繼續留在家避疫，公眾仍。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n本月中的30萬次。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯在過去24小時多10,899宗確診，累計232,243人染病，僅次於有逾130萬人確診的美國，是第二多人確診的國家。病例中。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n，但其餘人只有購物和放狗才可出門，進入商店購物及乘坐公共交通時須佩戴口罩和手套，外遊亦要事先取得電子許可。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200513/large/1589299626_1ddd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200513%2Flarge%2F1589299626_1ddd.gif&h=8039064f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防員在醫院前接受消毒。歐新社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑呼吸器致失火<br />\n<br />\n另外，聖彼德堡市專收武漢肺炎病人的聖喬治醫院昨失火，六樓起火，五名使用呼吸機的病人死亡，其中四人在深切治療部，另150。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n此外，上周末另一間位於首都莫斯科的抗疫醫院亦起火，導致一死，逾百人疏散；前日就有安老院火災，11人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n法新社／美聯社"},{"pid":"a038fc88f3a355fd8abb083ed624c893fe0ebe57","tid":2015180,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"呼吸機係咪支那機嚟"},{"pid":"caa052243bb1e6d0a10c21baeacd706c571ebee4","tid":2015180,"uid":22736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a038fc88f3a355fd8abb083ed624c893fe0ebe57","tid":2015180,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"呼吸機係咪支那機嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T13:14:37.000Z","msg":"係俄佬自己做"},{"pid":"0169bc83a77f0842aa0b54e4ea300f6d1504a792","tid":2015180,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"做鳩小習未呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4453301d469c7dd4eaa3e4d74e40d00b4fad8ea2","tid":2015180,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T13:18:19.000Z","msg":"多5個成功岀院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0d497158d36159074b1b67e58bb290c63644fd","tid":2015180,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T13:23:30.000Z","msg":"俄佬真係玩全民感染，汰弱留強。"},{"pid":"b6d9b4e848b5be56eb9505a873158336479e5535","tid":2015180,"uid":201751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T13:24:27.000Z","msg":"俄佬打柒你契弟未"},{"pid":"cd7babcc4bcc65c899b703c147543f90d279eb26","tid":2015180,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"tvb不會報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}